card_about_me: With over 10 years of experience, most part of it working with JavaScript, React, and React-Native. My experience has allowed me to develop a wide range of applications, from simple single-feature apps to complex enterprise software. I have experience with different Map API libraries, Payment gateway, e-Commerce platforms, ERP systems, and Cashback systems. I am well-versed in other related technologies, such as PHP and Node.js. Currently, I am working with payment and e-commerce platforms. Overall, I am confident in my ability to deliver robust and high-quality applications using JavaScript, Node.js, React, and React-Native.
